params.name: data.tensorboard_time_series
params.description: Required. The resource name of the TensorboardTimeSeries to export data from. Format: projects/{project}/locations/{location}/tensorboards/{tensorboard}/experiments/{experiment}/runs/{run}/timeSeries/{time_series}

params.name: data.filter
params.description: Exports the TensorboardTimeSeries' data that match the filter expression.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of data points to return per page. The default page_size will be 1000. Values must be between 1 and 10000. Values above 10000 will be coerced to 10000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: A page token, received from a previous [TensorboardService.ExportTensorboardTimeSeries][] call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to [TensorboardService.ExportTensorboardTimeSeries][] must match the call that provided the page token.

params.name: data.order_by
params.description: Field to use to sort the TensorboardTimeSeries' data. By default, TensorboardTimeSeries' data will be returned in a pseudo random order.
